OL,3,CSAS soldier who helped free Iranian
OL,4,CEmbassy hostages dies
OL,6,FITN correspondent Paul Davies reports
OL,7,Fon the 1980 siege on the Iranian
OL,8,Fembassy.
OL,10,FAn SAS soldier involved in the daring
OL,11,Fattack to free hostages from the
OL,12,FIranian Embassy has died at the age of
OL,13,F82.
OL,15,FLiverpool-born John Thompson served in
OL,16,Fthe Parachute Brigade and the renowned
OL,17,F22 SAS Regiment which stormed the
OL,18,FLondon embassy building in 1980.
OL,20,FHe died on Saturday, 31 August, at the
OL,21,Fage of 82.
