OL,6,FJohn's death was announced on the
OL,7,FFacebook page of the Parachute
OL,8,FRegiment and Airborne Forces Memorial
OL,9,FGroup.
OL,11,FA statement reads: "It is with great
OL,12,Fsadness that I share the news of the
OL,13,Fpassing of John Thompson last night.
OL,15,F"John was an extraordinary individual
OL,16,Fwhose impact on those around him will
OL,17,Fnot be forgotten...
OL,19,F"...John served with honor in the 16
OL,20,FParachute Brigade and the renowned 22
OL,21,FSAS Regiment.
