OL,6,F"He was a proud participant in
OL,7,FOperation Nimrod during the Iranian
OL,8,FEmbassy siege, showcasing his bravery
OL,9,Fand commitment to his country."
OL,11,FThe Iranian Embassy siege took place
OL,12,Ffrom 30 April to 5 May 1980, and was
OL,13,Ftelevised live on domestic television.
OL,15,FIt saw six armed SAS men, dressed in
OL,16,Fblack, storm the Embassy in South
OL,17,FKensington in London after
OL,18,Fnegotiations with the hostage takers
OL,19,Fhad reached stalemate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
