OL,4,CEmbassy hostages dies
OL,6,FThe gunmen inside were Iranian Arabs
OL,7,Fcampaigning for sovereignty of a
OL,8,Fprovince of Iran called Khuzestan.
OL,10,FThey had taken 26 people hostage and
OL,11,Fwere demanding prisoner releases and
OL,12,Ftheir own safe passage from the UK.
OL,14,FAs the siege developed into its sixth
OL,15,Fday, five hostages were released but
OL,16,Fas tension grew, one hostage was
OL,17,Fkilled and his body thrown out of the
OL,18,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
