OL,3,CSAS soldier who helped free Iranian
OL,4,CEmbassy hostages dies
OL,6,FIn a raid known as Operation Nimrod,
OL,7,Fthe SAS(Special Air Service) attacked
OL,8,Fthe Embassy to rescue the remaining
OL,9,Fhostages by abseiling from the roof
OL,10,Fand forcing entry through the windows.
OL,12,FIn total, the attack lasted just 17
OL,13,Fminutes and saw all but one of the
OL,14,Fremaining hostages freed and five of
OL,15,Fthe six hostage-takers killed.
OL,17,FJohn Thompson enlisted in the REME
OL,18,F(Royal Electrical Mechanical
OL,19,FEngineers) of the Parachute Brigade
OL,20,Fand later the SAS.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
