OL,6,FHe also served in the Falklands War
OL,7,Fand reached the rank of Warrant
OL,8,FOfficer. He later went on to serve in
OL,9,Fthe Omani Army.
OL,11,FAfter retiring from the forces, John
OL,12,Ftrekked to the Mount Everest Base
OL,13,FCamp, completed numerous marathons and
OL,14,Fultra marathons, and achieved a Black
OL,15,FBelt in martial arts.
OL,17,FHe spent his later years in Anglesey,
OL,18,FNorth Wales.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
