OL,6,F"Though he may no longer be with us,
OL,7,Fhis legacy will live on in the hearts
OL,8,Fand minds of everyone he touched.
OL,10,F"Rest in peace, John Thompson. Your
OL,11,Fbravery and spirit will never be
OL,12,Fforgotten."
